reviewText: LOVE THIS SEE MORE LIKE THIS

The video started out with Jessica posing on a bed while she was wearing lingerie. She removed as the video progressed. However, at times the video showed her with her lingerie back on. She did go completely nude, but never was photographed in any full frontal poses. However, there were a few full nude backside poses. The video also had an interview with questions on her of some of here likes and dislikes. A slide show of poses taken while she was being photographed during her video was also a selection option on the menu. The menu was hard to see as the color of the menu choices were close to the color of the background.

This is a nice artistic piece of work. However its only one nude film of a photo shoot. The other film is her interview.

I would not buy this series IMHO.
